foot
Homonym Number:
Word Class: verb
Sense Number:
Definition:[fencing] to place a piece of wood or other solid material at the foot of a post to ensure it remains vertical.


Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain: Rural
